    "System failures, caused by an insufficient understanding of LM weaknesses on core financial NLP tasks, will cause serious public harm and entail significant economic and legal consequences for businesses an financial institutions.",
    "We adopt the widely accepted meaning of holistic evaluation from Liang et al. (2022), which requires: (1) standardization, (2) recognition of incompleteness, and (3) multi-metric evaluation.",
    "Holistic benchmark suites help prevent these errors by identifying gaps in data coverage in their dataset taxonomy, encouraging comprehensive study of model behavior, and providing a reliable and repeatable method for comparison.",
    "However, no benchmark suites for evaluating core NLP finance tasks on LMs meet the definition of 'holistic.'",
    "In Table 1, we assess other existing benchmarks and highlight how they fail to meet the criteria for a holistic evaluation."
